content: Hey there. My name is Rakshith. I came here from the Rust discord server (Name is BlackJackHack there). I've already contributed to the compiler a couple of times on small issues here and there. Looking forward to making bigger contributions to the compiler. Looking for a mentor who can help me through this as I start contributing to the source code :D

Hi @Rakshith Ravi! If you need issues to work on, I think @DPC is eager to give out some :slight_smile:
As for mentoring, there is the #t-compiler/help channel where you can ask questions and hopefully find mentors.
you can DM me @Rakshith Ravi
